Subject: Audio Device Hardware (External Handsfree, Handphone) not detecting
Description: Previous Ticket No: 00426312 adding logs file there.
What_We_Know__c:
After installing an agent on the client machines. Users want to join Google meet link and they are stuck at this stage for 4 to 5 minutes. 
But when they plugged handsfree in the audio jack port, the issue resolved.
Solution_Comment__c: The issue has been resolved after updating the server and client versions.
